{"type": "article", "id": 49623, "title": "LVMH 集团利润大涨，以及，Zara 开了一家只能线上购买的“实体店” | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的新闻。", "date": "2018-01-26T02:20:58Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 44205, "name": "zara"}, {"id": 1330, "name": "ASOS"}, {"id": 16156, "name": "Acne Studios"}, {"id": 18579, "name": "OFF-WHITE"}, {"id": 47351, "name": "Byero"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 699895, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 31, "image": "img/article/article_show/20180126101150vWzgTQ6rCP7hy4IN.jpg", "contents": "<h3 nocleanhtml=\"true\">一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><a href=\"http://uk.fashionnetwork.com/news/Asos-bucks-the-trend-as-UK-US-and-Europe-all-see-surging-sales,940300.html#.WmoG25P1UzU\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>英国电商 ASOS 销售大涨</strong></a> | 在截止至 12 月 31 日的四个月里，ASOS 集团的总收入达到 8.084 亿英镑，增长了 28%。ASOS 在英国、美国和欧洲均实现了大幅度增长，此外，活跃客户数量也上涨了 19%，订单总量达到了 2020 万。</p><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/financial/lvmh-net-profit-rises-29-in-11128839/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>LVMH 集团去年净利润大涨 29%</b></a> | 受益于中国市场强劲的需求，奢侈品集团 LVMH 在 2017 年 10 月至 12 月的第四季度的营收好于预期，全年销售额大涨 13%，至 426 亿欧元，净利润上涨 29%，至 51.29 亿欧元。其中，以 LV 为主的时装皮具部门的收入占据了集团整体利润的一半以上，销售额上涨了 13%，至 154 亿欧元。&nbsp;</p><p><a href=\"http://uk.fashionnetwork.com/news/Zara-to-debut-first-store-dedicated-exclusively-to-online-orders,940528.html\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>Zara 开出第一家只能在线购买的实体店</strong></a> | 为了缓解店铺的拥挤状况，Zara 要在伦敦的 Westfield Stratford 商店里开设一家只能在线购买的快闪店。这家店铺约 200 平米，提供一系列男装和女装，但只能在线购买。店内的工作人员将随身携带平板电脑，帮助客户下单。这家店将一直持续至 5 月，它提供退换货服务。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180126011121lCEo8u6RepKv2DFt.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.681481\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p>Instagram 账号<a href=\"https://twitter.com/DropsByJay\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">@DropsbyJay</a> 爆料，Supreme 和 Vans 将合作推出鞋款，它会是一双有着绿色骷髅头图案的 Sk8-Hi。目前还没有透露出关于这双鞋的定价消息，但有不少传闻说它可能会在今年春天上市。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180126010743CXiShI6MtPbZfTYx.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>OFF-WHITE 和 Byredo 发布联名香水，取名<a href=\"https://www.highsnobiety.com/p/off-white-byredo-fragrance-perfume/\" rel=\"nofollow\">“Elevator Music”</a>。目前该香水的确切信息还未得到官方证实。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201801260110388ULaipkeMfYv2QT0.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"https://hypebae.com/2018/1/hello-kitty-puma-suede-collection\" rel=\"nofollow\">PUMA 和 Hello Kitty 出联名</a>，包括 T 恤、连帽衫、鞋子和包，同系列的单品还有儿童款，将于 2 月 8 日正式上架。 </p><p>这可能是你见过的最可爱的 PUMA。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180126101309VwCvYWsdn70XzlOZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180126101325BAUfPuWzGgJIraxl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180126101317iP53kWw8VKxI7p6s.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180126101317NHsx9qe2dDL73EXf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180126101317bvxeQ481uGZBVy0I.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180126101337KQgXiTvSUhOa971P.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201801261013587sUd3jiZNxFDm5zG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2018012610135837Y2DRglA8OiIJto.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180126101358yZKqwj29LoCAYzbk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\"><br></p><p>手工制作的彩虹针织衫、超大风衣、羊毛外套，<a href=\"http://wwd.com/runway/fall-2018/paris/acne/review/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Acne Studios </a>这一季像极了流浪的嬉皮士。设计师 Jonny Johansson 称，要把这一系列献给他最近搬到斯德哥尔摩以外的音乐人朋友。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180126010852SJ5br62kMFEfBUNW.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.565154\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180126010854aQrTKOYGkduDXiJW.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180126010855ENw764kcUn0DqbTI.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180126010857MRaeYUDK1OG0HpC7.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201801260108588Ly5hlQF3X1ik0UY.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180126010901zr0hbGsPpUL4nyjC.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180126010901Tz7I0jfLFsU23Wvc.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180126010902FdJ5SYClEMfaNyb4.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201801260109029vb7nR0VhBkoISZY.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180126010903F625NjtUMblYsfi7.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180126010904LebCVFB2IDsmRE9W.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201801260109040EDGbRV83Ipg9FeQ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180126010908F1KlsHkfPuSVTMth.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180126010910gX8jRaKePrGSZ9Wp.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180126010911T6z7M3kuFPYeQU5X.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502930\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180126010912QXsgPyivWjxboKw0.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180126010912H5D7nPMxob2Cl6WG.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201801260109138JaLZwzsCmfoUkv5.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>去年年末，NIGO 的品牌 Human Made 在东京目黑区青叶台新开了一家店，名为 offline store。<a href=\"http://www.honeyee.com/fashion/000907\" rel=\"nofollow\">日本媒体</a>偷偷前去看了看： </p><p>这家店外面看上去颇为隐蔽，铁栅栏上可以看到 Human Made 的品牌 logo，店内的装潢也很简单，可以看到一部分的 Human Made 2018 春夏系列新款已经上架了。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180126101417x3vG6LSRj5oN9Zdz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180126101419C3k8ZqurNUJ2zv6b.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180126101419Web0oTnGlc9qBhwO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2018012610